  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_18",
    "text": "五、抑扬",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.671909659205485,
      0.09975773122416988,
      0.7566041540633193,
      0.1145788798631894
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_2",
    "text": "早寒有怀",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.2476305706795725,
      0.1145788798631894,
      0.3194192377495463,
      0.12825994014536127
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_19",
    "text": "抑扬是古代诗歌传情达意产曲折美的一种常见 手法。抑是否定、贬损，扬是肯定、称颂。抑扬是指在 诗歌作品中对人物或事物、事件等采取的欲扬先抑或 欲抑先扬的手法，而使人物的性格或精神、事物的特 征、事件的性质等在前后对比中发变化，使情感内涵 形成反差，使叙述、抒情构成波折，从而吸引读者，增强 作品的感染。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5057471264367817,
      0.11799914493373237,
      0.9219600725952813,
      0.23200798061849792
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_3",
    "text": "孟浩然",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.2573099415204678,
      0.13168020521590423,
      0.30973986690865096,
      0.14479122131965227
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_4",
    "text": "木落雁南度，北风江上寒。 我家襄水曲，遥隔楚云端。 乡泪客中尽，归帆天际看。 迷津欲有问，平海夕漫漫。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.18471466021375277,
      0.1470713980333476,
      0.39120790481952006,
      0.21148639019524013
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_5",
    "text": "【注】 ①迷津：迷路。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1088929219600726,
      0.21319652273051162,
      0.2710223835450696,
      0.22801767136953113
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_6",
    "text": "这诗以“平海漫漫”作结，有何妙处？请简要 分析。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07582173825368017,
      0.22972780390480263,
      0.489614841701956,
      0.2610802337181132
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_20",
    "text": "典型例题",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.6678765880217786,
      0.2394185549380077,
      0.7598306110102844,
      0.2588000570044178
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_7",
    "text": "答：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10969953619681387,
      0.26336041043180847,
      0.4904214559386973,
      0.29528288442354284
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_21",
    "text": "【例26】 （2011·东考)阅读下这唐诗， 完成后面的题目。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5073603549102642,
      0.2667806755023514,
      0.9203468441217988,
      0.29813310531566195
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_8",
    "text": "四、前后照应",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.21859245815688647,
      0.2975630611372381,
      0.3484573502722323,
      0.31238420977625764
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_22",
    "text": "咏山泉",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.686428715466828,
      0.3004132820293573,
      0.741278483565235,
      0.31409434231152916
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_9",
    "text": "照应是指诗歌篇章间的伏笔照应，又叫呼应，是古 典诗歌常见的种结构形式。诗不论律诗还是绝 句，都应有头有尾，前后内容就要有内在联系，前面交 待过的话，后面得有照应；后边要照应的话，前边得先 有个交待，形成个有机的整体，这样，诗歌前后才能 贯串，情节连贯、脉络清晰、结构紧凑，使读者容易掌握 全诗的脉络。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07582173825368017,
      0.31580447484680063,
      0.49122807017543857,
      0.4298133105315662
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_23",
    "text": "储光羲",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.686428715466828,
      0.3169445632036483,
      0.7404718693284936,
      0.33062562348582014
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_24",
    "text": "山中有流水，借问不知名。 映地为天色，飞空作雨声。 转来深涧满，分出小池平。 恬淡无人见，年年长自清。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6146400483968542,
      0.3329058001995155,
      0.81387376487195,
      0.39618070400456035
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 18
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_25",
    "text": "结合全诗，简要分析“映地为天，飞空作声”的 妙处。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5073603549102642,
      0.39846088071825564,
      0.92115345835854,
      0.42924326635314236
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_10",
    "text": "尾照应，即开头与结尾的照应，这样照应使诗歌 在结构上有浑然一体之感，能更加突出主题，起到良好 的表达效果。在些诗歌中，诗往往采今昔、他 我、物我照应的式，来抒发自己或他人情感。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0750151240169389,
      0.43152344306683765,
      0.4920346844121799,
      0.49650847940715404
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 20
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_26",
    "text": "答：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5226860254083484,
      0.43209348724526153,
      0.9219600725952813,
      0.46401596123699584
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 21
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_27",
    "text": "应用体验",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.6670699737850373,
      0.47028644719965795,
      0.7606372252470256,
      0.4902379934444919
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 22
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_28",
    "text": "4.阅读下一首古诗，完成后面问题。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5081669691470054,
      0.49764856776400174,
      0.7904819520064529,
      0.5130397605814451
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 23
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_11",
    "text": "典型例题",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.23714458560193588,
      0.5039190537266638,
      0.3290986085904416,
      0.5227305116146501
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 24
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_29",
    "text": "次萧冰崖梅花韵",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.6549707602339181,
      0.5141798489382927,
      0.7840290381125227,
      0.5284309533988885
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 25
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_12",
    "text": "【例25】 阅读下律诗，回答下列问题。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11211937890703771,
      0.5307111301125838,
      0.4508973583383747,
      0.5455322787516033
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 26
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_30",
    "text": "[宋]赵希桐",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6767493446259326,
      0.5307111301125838,
      0.7678967533776971,
      0.5455322787516033
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 27
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_13",
    "text": "登快阁",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.25650332728372655,
      0.5478124554652986,
      0.31054648114539224,
      0.5614935157474704
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 28
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_31",
    "text": "冰姿琼骨净无瑕，竹外溪边处士②家。 若使牡丹开得早，有谁风雪看梅花?",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5823754789272031,
      0.5478124554652986,
      0.8606573906029441,
      0.5780247969217615
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 29
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_14",
    "text": "黄庭坚",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.2573099415204678,
      0.5637736924611657,
      0.30973986690865096,
      0.5780247969217615
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 30
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_15",
    "text": "痴儿了却公家事，快阁东西倚晚晴。 落木千山天远大，澄江一道月分明。 朱弦已为佳人绝，青眼聊因美酒横。 万里归船弄长笛，此心吾与白鸥盟。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14922363379713652,
      0.5803049736354567,
      0.41782617463198224,
      0.6435798774405016
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 31
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_32",
    "text": "【注】①这首诗是唱和萧冰崖的《梅花》诗而 作。②处士：指隐居的读书人。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5251058681185723,
      0.5803049736354567,
      0.9195402298850575,
      0.6110873592703434
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 32
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_33",
    "text": "三、四两句欲扬先抑，写得意味深长。请作简要 赏析。",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.5226860254083484,
      0.6127974918056149,
      0.9203468441217988,
      0.6441499216189255
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 33
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_16",
    "text": "律诗的尾讲究回呼照应，试分析这诗的联 和尾联是如何照应的。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07582173825368017,
      0.645860054154197,
      0.4904214559386973,
      0.6777825281459313
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 34
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_34",
    "text": "答：_",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5226860254083484,
      0.6481402308678923,
      0.9227666868320226,
      0.6794926606812028
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 35
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_42",
    "text": "2.审范围(区间）",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5065537406735229,
      0.7313666809177711,
      0.631578947368421,
      0.745047741199943
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 36
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_35",
    "text": "鉴赏表达技巧的审题、答题要领",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.127445049405122,
      0.7330768134530427,
      0.44363783020770314,
      0.7478979620920622
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 37
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_43",
    "text": "指鉴赏范围的大小。依照范围大小，可分为局部型 和全诗型。局部型是指对诗歌的某句某联（阕）等表 达技巧的判断，全诗型是对全诗的表达技巧的判断。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5218794111716072,
      0.7484680062704859,
      0.9219600725952813,
      0.7997719823286304
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 38
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_36",
    "text": "备考方法",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.2250453720508167,
      0.7530283596978766,
      0.34281105061504336,
      0.7701296850505914
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 39
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_37",
    "text": "这样学",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.25650332728372655,
      0.771839817585863,
      0.30973986690865096,
      0.7849508336896109
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 40
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_38",
    "text": "一、审题：审清五点要求",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.07582173825368017,
      0.7883710987601539,
      0.254890098810244,
      0.8031922473991734
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 41
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_44",
    "text": "3.审角度",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.5073603549102642,
      0.8031922473991734,
      0.579149021980238,
      0.8168733076813453
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "order": 42
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_39",
    "text": "表达技巧题题干语般包括题型、范围（区间）、 角度、数量、步骤等方面的要求。审题，就是要审清这 些要求。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0750151240169389,
      0.8060424682912926,
      0.4904214559386973,
      0.8550662676357418
